 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a>推出了她即将发行的单曲“ The Giver”的新变体 - 在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）：流行超新星，他感觉就像是“拖拉赛”女孩之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>本月初， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-teases-new-song-the-giver-by-sharing-hotline-number-with-fans-3838983">罗恩（Roan）通过指示她的粉丝称其为“ 620-468-8646”（或“ 620 hot-togo”），开始取笑新单曲“ The Giver”</a> 。对于那些拨打数字的人，可以通过按键盘上的数字来选择各种选择。迫切需要预订“与牙医的约会”的粉丝，两个是为那些希望“接触律师”的人，三个是报告“管道问题”，等等。</p><p>然后，她<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGOhO3EJVdV/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">开始在社交媒体上上传自己穿着西装的图像</a>，并告诉粉丝，他们可以预订<a href="https://chappellroan.redstarmerch.com/products/the-giver-7-vinyl-single-the-lawyer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“送礼者”的七英寸乙烯基“律师版”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3831028" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831028" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831028" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Chappell-Roan.jpg" alt="Chappell Roan仍然喜欢Fortnite" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Chappell-Roan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Chappell-Roan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Chappell-Roan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Chappell-Roan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Chappell-Roan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Chappell-Roan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831028" class="wp-caption-text">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）在2024年在舞台上讲话。信用：唱片学院的丽贝卡·萨普/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>昨晚（2月25日），罗恩（Roan）推出了她的“送礼者”角色的第二版，被称为“水管工”。她与船上的柱塞张贴了一张自己的照片，并告知粉丝，他们可以通过她的网站预订“送礼者”的“水管工”。她在标题中写道：“是的。表现出裂纹的回来。”</p><p>七英寸乙烯基将于8月18日发货。根据其官方描述，记录的A面将以“送礼者”为特色，而B旁边将以演示为“早上适合它”  - <a href="https://chappellroan.redstarmerch.com/products/the-giver-7-vinyl-single-the-plumber" target="_blank" rel="noopener">目前所有的预订都是售罄</a>，但可能会在将来开放更多。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGgil8mTxLA/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546