ww.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Matty-Healy@2000x1270.jpg" alt="1975年的Matty Healy" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Matty-Healy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Matty-Healy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Matty-Healy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Matty-Healy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Matty-Healy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Matty-Healy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3813627" class="wp-caption-text"> 1975年的马蒂·希利</figcaption></figure><p>汉森法官还允许该案在1975年的1975年Productions LLP（不是个人）和FSA之间进行，但有命令FSA支付100,000英镑的法律费用。</p><p>去年夏天的消息传出，该<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-sued-for-2-4million-by-good-vibes-festival-over-matty-healy-and-ross-macdonald-kiss-incident-3779403">乐队被节日组织者，Future Sound Asia（FSA）以240万美元（190万英镑）起诉</a>。这是因为后者声称1975年的Productions LLP违反了合同，四个乐队成员违反了护理义务。</p><p>乐队的代表埃德蒙·卡伦（Edmund Cullen） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-should-not-be-held-personally-responsible-for-malaysia-on-stage-kiss-high-court-hears-3839535">本月初称，当组织者与乐队的合同并要求法院签订合同时，FSA试图“将责任固定在个人身上”和“非常奇怪”和“相当奇怪</a>”和“很奇怪”的企图。对个人成员的索赔。</p><p>作为回应，代表FSA的安德鲁·伯恩斯（Andrew Burns）声称，成员“故意表现出一种挑战和挑衅马来西亚当局的方式”，结果，音乐节带来了“巨大损失”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3619867" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3619867" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3619867" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/matty-healy@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/matty-healy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/matty-healy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/